   NEW YORK -- Allegheny &amp; Western Energy Corp. said its
TEX-HEX Corp. unit completed two horizontal discoveries, the
Lane No. 4 and the Dickson No. 5, in the Austin Chalk field
in south Texas.
   The energy concern said the Lane No. 4 well tested at a
